# Swordjin Godot Development Progress

## Current Build Info
- Engine: Godot 4.4.1-stable (GL Compatibility)
- Target: Mobile PWA via HTML5 export
- Resolution: 640x360 (scales to mobile)

# v0.52 WIP — Skeleton Archer Added

### New Files
- `scripts/skeleton_archer.gd` + `scenes/skeleton_archer.tscn` — Ranged enemy
  - Keeps optimal distance (~170px), retreats if player too close
  - Yellow telegraph before firing, windup timer in _physics_process (no race)
  - Arrow projectile scene + script: flies straight, hits player or walls
  - Weak melee bash (60% arrow damage) if player enters melee hitbox
  - HP 25, speed 70, arrow damage 7, fire cooldown 2s
- `scripts/arrow.gd` + `scenes/projectiles/arrow.tscn` — Projectile
  - Direction + speed + damage parameters, 3s lifetime, auto-cleanup
  - Hits player → deals damage, hits wall → plays impact SFX
- `scripts/generate_arrow_sfx.py` — Bow fire + arrow hit + impact WAVs
- 3x new SFX added to AudioManager: `bow_fire`, `arrow_hit`, `arrow_impact`

### Modified
- `level_manager.gd` — spawns archers from chapter JSON (type: "skeleton_archer")
- `audio_manager.gd` — loads +3 new SFX (total 11)
- `chapter002.json` — 2 melee skeletons + 1 archer (replacing 3 melee)

